HEADWORD: Regarder
<hw>Re*gard"er</hw> <pr>(r?*g?rd"?r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>One who regards.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Eng. Forest law)</fld> <def>An officer appointed to
supervise the forest.</def> <rj><au>Cowell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Regardful</ent>⟦br⟧
